\newlabel{tab:camb_chi2}{{4}{23}{Reduced $\chi ^2$ benchmark of the DSC forward model against CAMB Planck-2018 $D_\ell ^{\rm TT}$, with a single overall amplitude as the only fit parameter and a 20\% per-$\ell $ error budget. Sensitivity to projection radius $R_{\rm shell}$ and lattice size $N_{\rm grid}$ supports the standing-wave interpretation of reviewer 1: the agreement depends on geometric choices, not on intrinsic physics}{table.4}{}}
